  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM1.3.3">
<l>amaivuṭai yaṟaneṟi muḻuvatu muyarvaṟa vuyarn</l>
<l>tamaivuṭai mutalkeṭa loṭiviṭai yaṟanila matuvā</l>
<l>mamaivuṭai yamararum yāvaiyum yāvarun tāṉā</l>
<l>mamaivuṭai nāraṇaṉ māyaiyai yaṟipavar yārē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Being high without being lofty on the whole path of befitting Dharma</l>
<l>he fully is the ground inmidst the befitting beginning [and] the destructive annihilation.</l>
<l>He is the befitting immortals, everything and everyone.</l>
<l>Who are those that will understand the Māyā of befitting Nāraṇaṉ.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
